                <h1>University faces hurdles in implementing recommendations from Bias and Hate Task Force </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/f151cbdd-74b3-4c9a-bc45-1e08be76fd68.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

